title: Battle for Helm's Deep: Awesome Custom Map - Total War: WARHAMMER Gameplay
description:
What can you do against such reckless hate?  A new power is rising and its the GreenSkins?  Grimgor rallies a force of 10,000 orcs to destroy the people of Bretonnia.  But Bretonnia does not stand alone, the wood elves send forces!  And Men and Elves fight together once more!!!!  This is a custom map for Total War: Warhammer, its really awesome you should try it out :P  Enjoy the Battle :D
